</div><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Butt Kicker Guide. Video: Aliaksandr Makatserchyk</figcaption></figure>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading">How To Do</h4>



<ol>
<li>Bend the right knee, pulling the heel toward the glute.</li>



<li>Lift the left arm.</li>



<li>Straighten the right leg.</li>



<li>Lower the left arm.</li>



<li>Hop from the left to the right foot.</li>



<li>Repeat the sequence on the other side.</li>



<li>Continue for the desired duration.</li>
</ol>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading">Tips</h4>



<ul>
<li>Flex the foot as you pull it upward. This further activates the hamstrings.</li>



<li>Reach the arms overhead to increase the exercise intensity.</li>



<li>Keep the upper body tall. For proper alignment, avoid leaning forward.</li>
</ul>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading">Optimal Sets And Reps</h4>



